author: adammurdoch
msg: - Added FileSystemManagerFactory, which takes care of assembling FileSystemManager instances,
and provides a simple entry point for VFS clients.
- Changed DefaultFileSystemManager, to fall back to a default provider for URLs with an unknown
scheme.  Uses the URL-backed provider as the default provider, unless overridden.

msg: Added a debug Ant task that writes out the details of a file.

msg: Added a file provider that is backed by java.net.URL instances.  Pretty rough at the moment.
